name: Fiorentina - Traditions EP
description:
*FREE DELIVERY*

The debut acoustic 3-Track EP from Norwich quartet "Fiorentina".  Recently labelled as "Ones to Watch" by Noize Makes Enemies Online Magazine and currently booking shows for the New Year.

They made their home debut on 19/02/2010 to a Sold Out Norwich Arts Centre (capacity: 300)

For more information, see:
myspace.com/fiorentinauk



Tracklisting:

1. How To Burn Bridges (4:01)
2. Greatest View (3:15)
3. This Time Last Year (3:07)

name: Darwin & The Dinosaur - English For The Hearing Impaired
description:
The highly acclaimed debut from Norwich-based pop punk trio "Darwin & The Dinosaur". Influenced by the likes of Saves The Day, Hot Water Music, Millencolin and The Get Up Kids.


For more info, see: myspace.com/darwinandthedinosaur


Tracklisting: 

1. Ins and Outs 
2. Live Together, Die Alone 
3. Bookends 
4. And Hope to Die 
5. Why is Canada Called Canada 
6. Welcome 
7. No Dice 
8. I Heart NZ 
9. While I'm Away

name: Science vs Romance - From The Back Seat EP
description:
The debut EP from Midlands alt. Indie band "Science vs Romance".

Released in 2008, the band toured with Circa Survive (USA) + Twin Atlantic with this release.

For more info, see: myspace.com/sciencevsromancemusic


Tracklisting:

1. The Cure (4:26)
2. No KO In Disco (3:31)
3. Aeroplane Arcade (5:44)
4. For Me (4:06)
5. Hold On (4:57)
6. Death Of A Martyr (4:35)
